{"tid":1042432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"老母好撚憎我，我可以點","createTime":"2019-03-01T14:22:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T15:30:08.000Z","uid":227257,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e89fe327d267a7dc7968e7ddf4546e219523cea","tid":1042432,"uid":227257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:22:20.000Z","msg":"老母由我出世到依家咁多年都好憎我，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係佢親生，佢當我仲差過街邊人<br />\n成日想趕走我，我唔明lo<br />\n講真果句，家務成日都係我做，每晚我煮飯，自己有工作<br />\n我更有買禮物俾佢想佢開心<br />\n咁都唔夠？好好同佢傾，佢就好惡咁鬧我，開始人身攻擊<br />\n講真我對住佢好攰<br />\n我自認我有d位可能做唔到佢想要既資格<br />\n我完全覺得呢個生我養我既阿媽好恐怖<br />\n我唔知應該點做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓豬依家20幾啦，就來頂唔順啦<br />\n去睇醫生，醫生係話我身體健康狀況唔係太好<br />\n我同阿媽講，佢話關佢咩事<br />\n當下我真系好傷心，心碎啦<br />\n原來我咁耐既努力都冇用，原來屋企人就係咁對我既<br />\n其他親戚咩都唔知，有事就鬧我唔生性，激襯阿媽發脾氣<br />\n我真心唔知點算啦<br />\n#此文純發洩心中唔舒服<br />\nP.s樓豬爸爸早幾年已經過身<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ce1b6031d3c1bf9873d96cfe44dfceefedeb59","tid":1042432,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"佢對其他人係咪咁"},{"pid":"c73ed43c93bfe874205d57cc517df081bcf7100b","tid":1042432,"uid":218407,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"幾同情樓主遭遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n系你老母"},{"pid":"d7ae3a4cd17e32b68311126debba219912a1f7ce","tid":1042432,"uid":227257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"07ce1b6031d3c1bf9873d96cfe44dfceefedeb59","tid":1042432,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"佢對其他人係咪咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:29:57.000Z","msg":"唔係，佢對其他人好好，對我就係另外一個人咁"},{"pid":"2c256176bd34d708f4cf8d6aec3f51fef30b6e3f","tid":1042432,"uid":227257,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c73ed43c93bfe874205d57cc517df081bcf7100b","tid":1042432,"uid":218407,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:27:29.000Z","msg":"幾同情樓主遭遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n系你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"😂😂下次寫返正確既系"},{"pid":"196718f89301a4bbdda93884d74a0f41f62bd9de","tid":1042432,"uid":84282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:39:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70a4381ba7a1a0f78020de4c67e780b906df033d","tid":1042432,"uid":146342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:43:28.000Z","msg":"離開會令你覺得唔開心嘅地方"},{"pid":"675d9cf85390c3772341456d68a459e60968cb66","tid":1042432,"uid":172306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:55:13.000Z","msg":"同佢攤開嚟傾一次"},{"pid":"72a5f75bf3d0f9686ac830ce8d5648a5585a7b95","tid":1042432,"uid":101625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T15:30:08.000Z","msg":"走"}]}